lsMessShower|title=Mills Mess Shower|access-date=October 24, 2016}}</ref> || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|45141}} || 45141<ref name=\"Inventing Tricks\"/><ref name=\"Drops\"/> || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|50505}} || Chase,<ref>Burns, Aidan. \"[http://geocities.ws/aidanjburns/chase.html The Chase]\", ''Aidan's Juggling Page''. Siteswap: 55050. Accessed: November 3, 2016.</ref> snake,<ref name=\"Orgfaq\"/><ref name=\"Xah\">Lee, Xah (2005). \"[http://xaharts.org/jj/siteswap.html Siteswap]\", ''[http://xahlee.info/math/math_index.html XahArts.org]''. Accessed: November 8, 2016.</ref><ref>{{Library of Juggling|balls=3|id=Snake|title=Snake|access-date=October 24, 2016}}</ref> etc.<ref name=\"Examples\"/><ref name=\"Phillips\"/> || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|51414}} || 51414<ref>\"[http://geocities.ws/aidanjburns/five1414.html Five One Four One Four]\", ''Aidan's Juggling Page''. Accessed: 11 10 2016.</ref> || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|52233}} || [[Rubenstein's Revenge]]<br/> and Romeo's Revenge<ref>{{Library of Juggling|balls=3|id=Romeo'sRevenge|title=Romeo's Revenge|access-date=October 24, 2016}}</ref> || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|52512}} || Boston shuffle,<ref>{{Library of Juggling|balls=3|id=BostonShuffle|title=Boston Shuffle|access-date=October 24, 2016}}</ref> \"baby\",<ref name=\"Orgfaq\"/> etc.<ref name=\"Phillips\"/><ref>{{Library of Juggling|balls=3|id=Peter'sShuffle|title=Peter's Shuffle|access-date=October 24, 2016}}</ref> || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|52512*}} || Burke's Slam,<ref>{{Library of Juggling|balls=3|id=Burke'sSlam|title=Burke's Slam|access-date=October 24, 2016}}</ref> (5251221525) || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|53133}} || Shuffler's mess<ref>{{Library of Juggling|balls=3|id=Shuffler'sMess|title=Shuffler's Mess|access-date=October 24, 2016}}</ref> || 3 || 5 || S\n|-\n| {{right|53444}} || Tennis<ref name=\"Xah\"/><ref>\"[http://geocities.ws/aidanjburns/tennis.html Four Ball Tennis]\", ''Aidan's Juggling Page''. Accessed: November 3, 2016.</ref> || 4 